Revision history for DBIO-SQLite

{{$NEXT}}
    - Initial release as standalone distribution extracted from DBIO core
    - DBIO::SQLite schema component and DBIO::SQLite::Storage driver
    - DBIO::SQLite::SQLMaker with SQLite-specific SQL generation
    - DBIO::SQLite::Loader for Schema::Loader SQLite introspection support
    - Fix bind parameter type affinity for untyped numeric values
    - Migrate test suite from DBICTest to DBIO::Test / DBIO::SQLite::Test
    - Rename all DBIC references to DBIO throughout
    - Replace Path::Class with DBIO::Util path helpers in Loader
    - Add replicated mode to SQLite test helper
    - Comprehensive POD documentation for all modules
    - Align POD with DBIO conventions (=attr, =method collectors)
    - Restore historical Loader provenance note
